items.title: Bump dep/libbacktrace from `d0f5e95` to `da7eff2`

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

items.body:
Bumps [dep/libbacktrace](https://github.com/ianlancetaylor/libbacktrace) from `d0f5e95` to `da7eff2`.
Commits
  • da7eff2 libbacktrace: unpack literals into output buffer
  • fd9442f libbacktrace: rewrite and simplify main zstd loop
  • c992dd8 libbacktrace: support zstd decompression
  • 8602fda libbacktrace: check for sys/link.h
  • 7409767 libbacktrace: don't exit Mach-O dyld library loop on one failure
  • bc78542 libbacktrace: don't let "make clean" remove allocfail.sh
  • b6ddb3a libbacktrace: replace fgrep with grep in configure script
  • 4d2dd0b libbacktrace: don't skip initial aligned byte in uncompressed block
  • 2446c66 libbacktrace: gather address ranges from skeleton units
  • 509f74a libbacktrace: initialize DWARF 5 fields of unit
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
